messages.message:
<!here> :wave: :yellow_heart: Heads-up! The `instabase-public` GCR migration to GAR will be taking place *this evening* Jan-13-2025 at *17:00 PST* */ 18:00 MST / 20:00 EST*.

This _should_ have no impact on normal operations or any customer environments, but as always - let me know if you find otherwise.

Note that this will *ONLY* be affecting images in `gcr.io/instabase-public (http://gcr.io/instabase-public)`. This is not an operation on any ECR repositories, nor any of our other (already migrated) GCR repos.

Thanks!
